of documentation, archiving, licencing and re-use ;

Task 1 concerns the delimitation of the focused FrameNet substructure, and its coherence verification, in order
to make the resulting structure more easily usable for inference and for automatic enrichment (with compatibility
with the original model);

Task 2 concerns all the lexical aspects: which lexemes can express the selected frames, how they map to external
resources, and how their semantic argument can be syntactically expressed, an information usable for automatic
pre-annotation on the corpus;
